title: For Sale:  Hour Thirteen Consignment Services!
postcontent:
Hour Thirteen Defense Solutions   



   One of the services we offer our clients is the ability to sell their guns through our shop. This provides several benefits over private sales or simply selling straight out to a gun store.



    - Money! On a good day, the average gun store might offer you 50-60% of market value for your weapon. They're making an investment by purchasing your gun, to be viable, they must maintain a generous profit margin. Our consignment service costs 10% of the sale price, and we don't get paid till your gun sells. You pay NOTHING out of pocket.


    - Safety. We don't fear-monger here, most private sales go smoothly. But the notion of meeting somebody in a parking lot to swap gun for cash... Certainly leaves something to be desired.


    - Quick sale. Truth is, a huge portion of the used-gun purchases made, are by first-time gun buyers. These are the people who are NOT likely to feel comfortable meeting a seller in a parking lot. By selling through us, you have vastly expanded the range of people who will be looking at buying YOUR gun, not to mention our ability to sell and ship your weapon nation-wide.


    - Convenience. No more phone calls, emails, or texts to answer. No lowballers, or idiots wanting to trade a refrigerator for your gun. You send or bring the gun in, we handle it from there. When it sells, you get your money. Easy peasy.



Consignments can be applied for any use you'd like!



    - Good old Cash!

    - Special-Order or in-stock Firearms!

    - Bulk Ammo!

    - For clients starting the build of an Hour13 Carbine or 1911, you have the option to apply your consignments directly to your new build. For these sales, the 10% consignment fee is reduced to 5%! We have had many of our clients fund complete custom builds just with their consignment items!
